OL,3,C'There's No Safety Net': London Boat
OL,4,CDweller Struggles to Access GP
OL,6,FWhile living on a canal boat can offer
OL,7,Ffreedom and affordability, many boat
OL,8,Fdwellers in London struggle to
OL,9,Fregister with a GP because they lack a
OL,10,Ffixed address, according to the the
OL,11,FNational Bargee Travellers Association
OL,12,F(NBTA).
OL,14,FNHS guidance states that people do not
OL,15,Fneed proof of address to register with
OL,16,Fa GP practice. However, campaigners
OL,17,Fsay those living on boats with no
OL,18,Fpermanent mooring and others without
OL,19,Faddresses often encounter difficulties.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
