PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773765957
OL,3,C'There's No Safety Net': London Boat
OL,4,CDweller Struggles to Access GP
OL,6,FCanal boat owner Camille Tsang had
OL,7,Fbeen registered with a GP surgery near
OL,8,Fher office in Colindale, North London,
OL,9,Fwhere she has worked for more than 10
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FIn September 2024, she received a
OL,13,Fletter from Colindale Medical Centre
OL,14,Finforming her that she had been
OL,15,Fremoved from their patient list and
OL,16,Fadvising her to register with a local
OL,17,FGP.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773765957
OL,3,C'There's No Safety Net': London Boat
OL,4,CDweller Struggles to Access GP
OL,6,FDespite working and paying regular
OL,7,FNational Insurance contributions,
OL,8,FCamille says she has been fighting to
OL,9,Faccess a GP ever since.
OL,11,F"The problem is I don't have a
OL,12,Fcatchment area," she said. "There's no
OL,13,Fsafety net for me. If I were to get
OL,14,Fsick for more than a week and needed a
OL,15,Fsick note, I wouldn't be able to get
OL,16,Fone."
OL,18,FCamille raised the issue with her
OL,19,Flocal NHS care board and later took
OL,20,Fher complaint to the Parliamentary
OL,21,FHealth and Service Ombudsman.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,410,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773765957
OL,3,C'There's No Safety Net': London Boat
OL,4,CDweller Struggles to Access GP
OL,6,FMarcus Trower, secretary of the NBTA,
OL,7,Fsaid this is a common issue for boat
OL,8,Fdwellers.
OL,10,FHe is calling for harsher
OL,11,Frepercussions for GP practices that
OL,12,Frefuse to register patients without a
OL,13,Ffixed address.
OL,15,F"There needs to be some kind of
OL,16,Fconsequences for GPs denying somebody
OL,17,Fhealthcare," he said. "Surely we
OL,18,Fshould all be able to access
OL,19,Fhealthcare."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
