PN,40905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1773765957
OL,3,C'There's No Safety Net': London Boat
OL,4,CDweller Struggles to Access GP
OL,6,FIn a statement, NHS North Central
OL,7,FLondon Integrated Care Board told ITV
OL,8,FNews:
OL,10,F"We understand how important it is to
OL,11,Fbe able to access health and care
OL,12,Fservices. We sincerely apologise for
OL,13,Fthe significant delay Ms Tsang has
OL,14,Fexperienced in resolving this and
OL,15,Funderstand how worrying and
OL,16,Ffrustrating this must have been. We
OL,17,Fare urgently working with her former
OL,18,FGP to find a solution."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
